// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0765 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: d59b3e1a-2c1d-5b12-bafb-fcaa8c778784

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:18.04-ESM*)
